message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech signal analysis and content-dependent speaker comparison. cs.LG is also likely as deep neural networks are used in the experiments. cs.SI is another possibility as the paper deals with signal processing techniques. cs.SD is more likely than cs.SI as the focus is on speech signals rather than general signal processing. cs.CL is less likely as the paper does not deal with natural language processing or text analysis.
